leve.name: Earth Sprites Are Easy
leve.description: Sprite-based products enjoy a healthy following, and never more so than since the Calamity. Rocks from areas favored by earth sprites are popular as “companion cobbles,” oversized amulets of a sort. Delivery may be made to the accounting department of Amajina & Sons, care of Shushunen Bubunen.
leve.client: East Aldenard Trading Accountant, Shushunen Bubunen
